SHOW
  Display statistics and build requirements for unit types.

SYNTAX
  show <type> [build|capability|stats]

DESCRIPTION
  Shows detailed information about ship, plane, land unit, or
  sector types.

  <type>:
    s  ship        p  plane       l  land unit
    b  bridge      n  nuke

  Sub-commands:
    build       - materials, cost, tech required to build
    capability  - what the unit can do (flags like FISH, TORP, etc.)
    stats       - combat and movement statistics

  Use this before building to check requirements.

EXAMPLE
  show s b                  ship build requirements (all types)
  show s c                  ship capabilities
  show l b                  land unit build requirements
  show p b                  plane build requirements

SEE ALSO
  build  designate  sector-types  census
